("750","1","2021-12-14 08:46:01","2021-12-14 08:46:01","<div class=\"style_thumbnailDescription__syRES style_ph50__1qq92\">\r\n<div class=\"style_textDescription__6qQQe\">Tm hiu nhng ct mc mi trn h sinh thi v nhng cp nht mi nht v cc d n ang pht trin trn Serum.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"post-detail-content\" class=\"style_postContentWrapper__2goJG style_ph50__1qq92 style_fontMedium__1ecko\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-0\">t SRM &amp; Khi lng giao dch 24H</h2>\r\nTun qua, Serum  t 247K SRM, theo t gi hin ti tng ng 1 triu USD. ng thi, khi lng giao dch 24H ca Serum cng t 350 triu USD.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\">Miami Hacker House</h2>\r\nC hi cui  tham gia xy dng d n trn Project Serum v ginh gii thng ca Hacker House!\r\n<div>\r\n<figure><a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/hinh-2.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-753\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/hinh-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"618\" height=\"406\" /></a></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\">Bonfida x Serum Core</h2>\r\nNh AOB, Serum tr thnh mt nn tng m bt k protocol, d n phi sinh (derivative) hay giao ngay (spot) no cng c th s dng. Cc team dev cng c th dng n  kt hp vi bt k th g - ngay c NFT hay tn min.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\">Zeta Market Fundraising</h2>\r\nZeta Markets trn Serum va cng b gi c $8.5 M trong vng Funding Round, dn u bi JumpCapital v nhng nh u t tim nng khc.\r\n<div>\r\n<figure><a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/hinh-3.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-755\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/hinh-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"578\" height=\"544\" /></a></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\">Switchboard V2 Beta</h2>\r\nVi Switchboard v2, cc nh pht trin Solana khng cn cn nhn ti tr hay ku gi h tr xy dng cc feed. Serum ang hng n thi im ni chng ti c th a d liu on-chain qua mng oracle phi tp trung ca Switchboard.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\">Messari ni v Project Serum</h2>\r\nD n c xy dng  gii quyt nhiu vn  trong khng gian DeFi m nhm  gp vo thi im : nhng hn ch ca Ethereum khin n chm v tn km, nhiu protocol trn thc t vn mang tnh tp trung v vn cn thiu chc nng cross-chain.\r\n<div>\r\n<figure><a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/hinh-4.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-757\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/hinh-4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"678\" height=\"648\" /></a></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">To lp th trng trn Mango</h2>\r\nBn  bit tin g cha? Ph giao dch ti cc th trng c to lp trn Serum u  gim!\r\n\r\nNu bn bn Mango Perpetual (chit khu ca nh sn xut 4 bps - im c bn) v mua giao ngay (ph ngi mua 2.4 bps) vi cng mc gi, bn s nhn c li nhun 1.6% bps.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\">Tch hp AVAX vo mng Pyth</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<figure><a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/hinh-5.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-759\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/hinh-5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"601\" height=\"484\" /></a></figure>\r\n</div>\r\nAVAX - token gc ca blockchain Avalanche nay  c mt trn mng Pyth.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-8\">Mng Pyth hp tc vi Talos Trading</h2>\r\nVic cc t chc p dng ti sn k thut s ang din ra kh tt vo thi im ny, nhng chng ti cng bt u thy l cc t chc ny cng ang p dng DeFi. Chng ti rt vui mng khi tr thnh mt phn ca Serum  gip thc y hn na s pht trin ca c s h tng DeFi v khin h thng ti chnh ca chng ti tr nn hiu qu v minh bch hn - Anton Katz, ng sng lp v Gim c iu hnh ca Talos ni.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-9\">Ai ang xy dng trn Serum?</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<figure><a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/hinh-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-751\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/hinh-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"393\" /></a></figure>\r\n</div>\r\nDanh sch ny khng y  nhng hy vng cho cc bn thy c mt s d n th v ang xy dng trn h sinh thi Serum.\r\n\r\n</div>","Cp nht mi nht trn Serum","","publish","open","open","","cap-nhat-moi-nhat-tren-serum","","","2021-12-18 02:13:24","2021-12-18 02:13:24","","0","https://askventure.asia/?p=750","0","post","","0"),
("764","1","2021-12-12 08:52:42","2021-12-12 08:52:42","<div class=\"style_thumbnailDescription__syRES style_ph50__1qq92\">\r\n<div class=\"style_textDescription__6qQQe\">Anyswap chnh thc thng bo v vic i tn d n thnh Multichain vi tm nhn mi. Chi tit ti y!</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"post-detail-content\" class=\"style_postContentWrapper__2goJG style_ph50__1qq92 style_fontMedium__1ecko\">\r\n\r\nc thnh lp vo thng 7 nm 2020, tin thn l Anyswap  nh v cho mnh tr thnh mt sn DEX a chui ( cross-chain DEX). Vo u nm 2021, nm bt c nhng thay i ng k trong th trng, Anyswap  chuyn s tp trung pht trin sang cc dch v v cu ni a chui (cross-chain bridge, NFT bridge).\r\n\r\n c th nh v r hn vai tr ca mnh, Anyswap quyt nh i tn thng hiu thnh Multichain. Multichain k tha nhng thnh tu m Anyswap  t c cng vi mt din mo cng nh tm nhn mi. Multichain gi y tr thnh c s h tng dn u cho h sinh thi a chui.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-0\"><strong>Multichain - Giao thc nh tuyn a chui</strong></h2>\r\nMultichain l mt giao thc nh tuyn a chui (a Cross-Chain Router Protocol CRP), mt c s h tng c thit k  kt ni xuyn sut nhng ti sn a chui v hn th na cung cp cc cng c pht trin cross-chain cho bn th ba. Hng ti mc ch tr thnh b nh tuyt u vit nht dnh cho<strong>Web3</strong>.\r\n\r\nMultichain hin dn u vi cc li th nh bo mt, tc  v tri nghim cho ngi dng. V lnh vc bo mt, thnh phn quan trng nht l m hnh tnh ton a bn, ch k ngng (Multi-party Computation,Threshold Signature Scheme) v khng gim st (MPC/TSS + Non-Custodial). y cng chnh l cng ngh ct li ca Multichain trong vic m bo cc ti sn trn chui (onchain). Multichain n nay c cho l gii php tt nht trong cc giao thc chui cho vi tng TVL gn 5 t  la. Vt qua nhiu vng kim tra bo mt bi cc cng ty bo mt hng u th gii nh TrialOfBits, Slowmist v PeckShield.\r\n\r\nMi ngi c th tham kho cc bo co bo mt ti y:<strong><a href=\"https://github.com/anyswap/Anyswap-Audit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://github.com/anyswap/Anyswap-Audit</a></strong>\r\n\r\n tng cng hn na nhng bin php bo mt, Multichain  thit lp qu bo mt (Security Funds)  m bo s hot ng xuyn sut ca h thng cng nh trong trng hp c s c bt ng xy ra.\r\n\r\nNhng nng cp n tng gn y  tng tc  ca giao dch a chui ln 4 ln, tc  trung bnh dao ng trong khong 100 giy, mt ci tin ng k ca giao thc.  to thun li hn na cho ngi dng, Multichain  n gin ha v kt hp giao din ngi dng, Cu ni (BridgeV2) gi y  c hp nht vi B nh Tuyn (RouterV3), ch c 1 mc duy nht  thc hin cc giao dch chui cho (Cross-chain Swap). Multichain ng thi gii thiu h thng h tr ngi dng Zendesk hot ng 24/7.\r\n<h3 id=\"section-1\"><strong>MULTI Tokenomics</strong></h3>\r\nMULTI s thay th ANY  lm token qun tr (Governance Token) cho giao thc CRP. N cho php ch s hu MULTI tham gia vo vic qun l h sinh thi v cng ng thng qua b phiu.\r\n\r\nMultichain c nh v li nh c s h tng c bn cho Web3, tng kh nng tng tc ti sn trn chui, ng thi cung cp cc cng c cn thit cho cc nh pht trin xy dng cc ng dng multichain dapp nh multichain lending, multichain dex, multichain farming...\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><strong>Tng cung MULTI:</strong>100,000,000 (1:1 vi ANY).</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Cung lu hnh:</strong>18,639,320chim (18,64% tng cung).</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nMULTI token khng lu hnh b kha trong<strong>hp ng thng minh</strong>. Trong tng lai s c cc d tho v b phiu trong vic s dng cng nh phn b mt cch hp l nht. Cho n lc , Token khng lu hnh s khng c m kha.\r\n<h3 id=\"section-2\"><strong>Chuyn i ANY thnh MULTI</strong></h3>\r\ny l mt s hon i mt chiu  chuyn i ANY token thnh MULTI token. Khng c gii hn thi gian no c t ra cho vic chuyn i, nhng lu  rng khi qu trnh chuyn i hon tt, token ANY s b kha trong hp ng thng minh, v vy mnh khuyn anh em nn hon thnh cng sm cng tt trong trng hp xy ra mt mt khng ng c.\r\n\r\nVic chuyn i s ch c thc hin bi ngi nm d ANY token.\r\n\r\nT l c nh ANY: MULTI = 1: 1.\r\n\r\nMultichain s sm thng bo K hoch chuyn i.\r\n\r\n bit chi tit, anh em truy cp trang web chnh thc ca Multichain: https://multichain.org\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\">ng k cho d n ca bn trn Multichain</h2>\r\nMultichain mong mun tr thnh i tc vi cc nh pht trin cng nh d n tim nng  pht trin h sinh thi a chui thng qua vic cung cp v t vn cc dch v v cu ni min ph\r\n\r\nLink tham gia:<strong><a href=\"https://dard6erxu8t.typeform.com/to/C7RwF08A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Click Here</a></strong>\r\n<h3 id=\"section-4\">Hng dn s dng</h3>\r\nMultichain  c ti u ha  mang li tri nghim ngi dng mt cch tt hn. Tham kho hng dn s dng:<strong><a href=\"https://docs.multichain.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://docs.multichain.org/</a></strong>\r\n\r\nVic i thng hiu khng lin quan n bt k thay i no i vi nh iu hnh, cc dch v ang c s dng, cng khng nh hng n cc i tc ban u. Cc cam kt v sn phm v dch v ban u khng thay i.\r\n\r\nTrang web chnh thc ca Multichain hin ang hot ng.\r\n\r\nTrang web ban u ca Anyswap s tip tc cung cp dch v, tuy nhin n s khng cn c cp nht na.\r\n\r\n</div>","Anyswap chnh thc i tn d n (rebrand) thnh Multichain","","publish","open","open","","anyswap-chinh-thuc-doi-ten-du-an-rebrand-thanh-multichain","","","2021-12-18 02:13:33","2021-12-18 02:13:33","","0","https://askventure.asia/?p=764","0","post","","0"),
