("810","1","2021-12-17 09:36:34","2021-12-17 09:36:34","<div class=\"style_thumbnailDescription__syRES style_ph50__1qq92\">\r\n<div class=\"style_textDescription__6qQQe\">\r\n<div class=\"style_thumbnailDescription__syRES style_ph50__1qq92\">\r\n<div class=\"style_textDescription__6qQQe\">Bi vit gip anh em hiu thm v nh ngha, vai tr ca Whitepaper trong vic u t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"post-detail-content\" class=\"style_postContentWrapper__2goJG style_ph50__1qq92 style_fontMedium__1ecko\">\r\n\r\nAnh em thng c nhng g khi tm c mt d n mi? Twitter, Medium hay website? Tt c u ng. Nhng c mt nhn vt khc cng kh quan trng m mnh ngh nhiu ngi cng  bit, nhng cha tht s hiu r v nh ngha hay vai tr,  l White Paper.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-0\">White Paper l g?</h2>\r\nWhite Paper l ti liu dng  m t cc thuc tnh ca d n mt cch chun nht, gip cng ng c ci nhn tng quan v d n. White Paper l ngun thng tin chun nht nu cn tham kho v bt k d n no.\r\n\r\nThut ng White Paper ra i trc khi c s dng trong Crypto. White Paper c ngun gc cch y khong mt th k,  ch bo co ngnh c xut bn bi mt s b ca chnh ph Vng quc Anh. Cn i vi Crypto, Whitepaper c l c bit n sm nht vo thi k ICO (<strong>Initial Coin Offering</strong>).\r\n<div>\r\n<figure><a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/LGMRF3NJSR.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-815\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/LGMRF3NJSR.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"736\" height=\"413\" /></a><figcaption>White Paper l g?</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\">White Paper cha nhng thng tin g?</h2>\r\nDi y l mt s thng tin thng thy ca mt White Paper ca cc d n trong Crypto:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>nh ngha v d n:</strong>Tm tt s lt nht ca mt d n.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>L do ra i ca d n:</strong>Gii quyt vn  no  ca th trng.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>C ch hot ng ca d n:</strong>Nu cc thnh phn, vai tr ca tng thnh phn trong d n, cc cng thc s dng trong hot ng,...</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>L trnh pht trin:</