("836","1","2021-12-17 09:52:06","2021-12-17 09:52:06","<div class=\"style_thumbnailDescription__syRES style_ph50__1qq92\">\r\n<div class=\"style_textDescription__6qQQe\">Trong bi vit ny, chng ta s tm hiu tng quan v Proof of Concept (PoC), nhng li ch ca PoC mang li, cng nh ng dng ca n trong Blockchain.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"post-detail-content\" class=\"style_postContentWrapper__2goJG style_ph50__1qq92 style_fontMedium__1ecko\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-0\">Proof of Concept (PoC) l g?</h2>\r\nProof of Concept (PoC) hay c th gi l bng chng v khi nim. PoC  cp n vic trin khai th nghim mt  tng,  c th chng minh tnh kh thi ca  tng  trong thc t. Hiu theo cch khc, PoC l mt hnh thc tin hnh th nghim mt phng php hoc mt  tng no   chng minh tnh kh thi ca n. Trong i sng thc t, PoC thng c dng  chng minh cc l thuyt hoc gi thuyt, xem n c tnh thc tin vi i sng xung quanh hoc tc ng ti con ngi hay khng.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_837\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1300\"]<a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/A9S1E3N2TA.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-837 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/A9S1E3N2TA.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1300\" height=\"667\" /></a> Proof of Concept (PoC)[/caption]\r\n<h2>Lch s ra i ca Proof of Concept</h2>\r\nCm t Proof of Concept hay PoC ra i kh sm trc y, n c  cp chnh thc trong t in Oxford English thng 1/1967 bi Los Angeles Times. Nhng mt trong nhng cch s dng ban u ca PoC c  xut trong bi bo ca Bruce Carsten trn tp ch Conversion and Intelligent Motion.\r\n\r\nBan u, PoC l thut ng thng c s dng trong gii khoa hc k thut  chng minh v th nghim cc gi thuyt, xem xt tnh kh thi ca cc  tng  trong vic pht trin cc phn cng &amp; phn mm.\r\n\r\nTuy nhin, trong thi im hin ti th n khng cn b hp trong lnh vc khoa hc k thut na m m rng v ng dng trong nhiu ngnh ngh khc nhau nh lm phim, k s, bo mt, kinh doanh,...\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\">Li ch ca Proof of Concept (PoC) mang li</h2>\r\nVic ng dng Proof of Concept vo thc t mang li nhng li ch ng k cho cc bn t chc lin quan:\r\n\r\nLi ch u tin l tit kim thi gian v trnh mt qu nhiu cng sc, tin bc vo nhng  tng khng kh thi. T , chng ta c th tp trung ngun lc (nhn lc, tin bc, thi gian,..) vo cc  tng kh thi v tng kh nng thnh cng khi trin khai trong thc t.\r\n\r\nNgoi ra, vic trin khai PoC s gip bn c cn c v c s  c th tranh lun vi nh u t hay cc bn lin quan v  tng hay gi thuyt ca mnh, y s l iu gip ch ng  cho bn tranh lun v bin chng v tnh kh thi ca  tng.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\">ng dng ca Proof of Concept (PoC) trong Blockchain</h2>\r\nTng quan, Proof of Concept trong blockchain l mt qu trnh xc nh xem mt  tng d n<strong>Blockchain</strong>c th kh thi trong tnh hung thc t hay khng.\r\n\r\n<strong>Hy ly mt v d gin nh sau:</strong>\r\n\r\n<em>Bn v nhm ca mnh c  tng v vic xy dng mt sn giao dch trn cc Public Blockchain, cho php bt k ai c kt ni Internet cng c th giao dch. Vi  tng ny, u tin bn s cn quan tm v la chn mt s th:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><em>Vn  u tin bn cn quan tm l Blockchain no s h tr vic ny. C kh nhiu blockchain trn th trng nhng ch mt s trong  mi h tr<strong>smart contract</strong>.</em></li>\r\n 	<li><em>Tip theo l ngn ng lp trnh h tr, a phn cc nn smart contract platform s c cc ngn ng lp trnh ring, liu ngn ng m platform  h tr c phi l ngn ng m bn hay nhm ca bn thnh tho?</em></li>\r\n 	<li><em>Tip theo, liu platform m bn chn c tool h tr c vic xy dng ng dng nh yu cu ca bn hay bn phi xy dng t con s 0. Vic xy dng t s khng s tn rt nhiu ti nguyn (cng sc, thi gian v tin bn).</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Chi tit hn, c cho l bn  gii quyt nhng vn  c bn c   trn, s cn c cc vn  lin quan chuyn su hn n vic xy dng mt sn giao dch:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><em>Bn v nhm ca bn s chn kin trc cho sn giao dch nh th no. N l mt sn Orderbook, AMM, hay loi kin trc no khc?</em></li>\r\n 	<li><em><strong>Tokenomics</strong>ca d n s c thit k nh th no?</em></li>\r\n 	<li><em>Lm sao  d n ca bn th thu ht c thanh khon v ngi dng t cc sn giao dch khc trn th trng?</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nT kin thc, kinh nghim v li th ring ca bn hoc nhm ca bn, bn s chn ra mt hay mt vi la chn ph hp. Sau , s bt u la chn, tm hiu v xy dng.\r\n\r\nS thnh cng ca<strong>DeFi</strong>(Decentralized Finance) l mt trong nhng v d in hnh v vic ng dng cng ngh Blockchain vo Finance, nhng  c c thnh cng nh hin nay, cc nh pht trin  dnh rt nhiu thi gian  nghin cu, th nghim v tm kim ra cc m hnh c th thnh cng trong thc t, y c th xem l ng dng ca PoC trong thc t.\r\n\r\nTrong thc t, c rt nhiu mng ng dng tim nng trong thc t m chng ta c th khai thc nh vo cng ngh blockchain nh hnh bn di:\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_839\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1300\"]<a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/N3828N4LEG.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-839 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/N3828N4LEG.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1300\" height=\"355\" /></a> Cc ngnh tim nng c th trin khai trn Blockchain[/caption]\r\n\r\nVi s pht trin v i mi trong khng gian blockchain, s c rt nhiu ngnh cng nghip truyn thng s b nh hng. C nhn mnh tin rng s c nhiu ngi hiu tm quan trng ca vic ny. Nhng vn  l a phn h khng thc s bit cch bt u vi blockchain t u. Hn na, h c th khng c ngn sch khng gii hn cho nhng th nghim ko di khng thnh cng, v vy tip cn vn  vi PoC l mt cch khn ngoan trc khi bc vo qu trnh th nghim trong thc t.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\">Tng kt</h2>\r\nMnh hy vng cc ni dung ny s gip cc bn c th nm bt c nhng thng tin tng quan v Proof of Concept (PoC), cng nh cc ng dng ca PoC trong Blockchain.\r\n\r\n</div>","Proof of Concept (PoC) l g? ng dng ca PoC trong Blockchain","","publish","open","open","","proof-of-concept-poc-la-gi-ung-dung-cua-poc-trong-blockchain","","","2021-12-18 02:05:29","2021-12-18 02:05:29","","0","https://askventure.asia/?p=836","0","post","","0"),
