("921","1","2021-12-18 01:59:40","2021-12-18 01:59:40","<strong>Hn 90% tng s Bitcoin tn ti  c khai thc. Khi mng li tin t ngy cng nng cao nhn thc v s dng trn ton th gii, thc y nhu cu ngy cng tng i vi BTC.</strong>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_117984\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-117984\"><a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/bitcoin-flash-crash.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-778\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/bitcoin-flash-crash.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1365\" height=\"800\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-117984\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S Bitcoin d tr trn sn giao dch chm y mc d 90% ngun cung BTC  c khai thc</figcaption></figure>\r\nTheo s liu t CoinMarketCap, tnh n sng ngy 13/12, s lng Bitcoin c khai thc  t n con s 18.899.537 n v, chim 90%tng cung 21 triu BTC ca Bitcoin.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Bitcoin-90-percent-supply-13.12.21.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-776\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Bitcoin-90-percent-supply-13.12.21.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1536\" height=\"584\" /></a>\r\n\r\nVi hn 90% ngun cung Bitcoin  c pht hnh, s khan him thm ch cn r rng hn trong hin ti. S tht l hu ht ngun cung BTC ang lu thng c nm gi bi cc t chc ln v khng h c  nh mun bn BTC trong ngn hn, mc d cckhon u t t  ca h u  x2trong t tng gi va qua.\r\n<div class=\"twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered\"><iframe id=\"twitter-widget-0\" class=\"\" title=\"Twitter Tweet\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/embed/Tweet.html?creatorScreenName=coin68&amp;dnt=false&amp;embedId=twitter-widget-0&amp;features=eyJ0ZndfZXhwZXJpbWVudHNfY29va2llX2V4cGlyYXRpb24iOnsiYnVja2V0IjoxMjA5NjAwLCJ2ZXJzaW9uIjpudWxsfSwidGZ3X2hvcml6b25fdHdlZXRfZW1iZWRfOTU1NSI6eyJidWNrZXQiOiJodGUiLCJ2ZXJzaW9uIjpudWxsfSwidGZ3X3NwYWNlX2NhcmQiOnsiYnVja2V0Ijoib2ZmIiwidmVyc2lvbiI6bnVsbH19&amp;frame=false&amp;hideCard=false&amp;hideThread=false&amp;id=1470157796679331848&amp;lang=vi&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fcoin68.com%2Fbitcoin-cham-day-90-nguon-cung-btc-khai-thac%2F&amp;sessionId=55009543af25e6f687e36817b50f21b4b209bab3&amp;siteScreenName=coin68&amp;theme=light&amp;widgetsVersion=9fd78d5%3A1638479056965&amp;width=550px\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-tweet-id=\"1470157796679331848\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nC th k n nhng tay to hng u trn th trng nh MicroStrategy, cng ty ang ng u bng xp hng vi 122.477 BTC, tr gi c tnh 5,9 t USD. Tesla ng  v tr th hai 43.200 BTC, khong 2 t USD. Square (nay  i tn thnh Block) caJack Dorsey, xp  v tr th ba vi 8.027 BTC, tng ng khong 387 triu USD.\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_117836\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-117836\"><a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/hyt.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-784\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/hyt.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1266\" height=\"709\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-117836\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cc khon u t v nm gi Bitcoin ca nhiu ng ln hng u. Ngun: Bitcoin Treasuries</figcaption></figure>\r\nMt s cng ty khai thc Bitcoin ln nht trn th gii cng  bt tay vo cuc chi t chc trong nm nay, em v thnh cng rt ln trn c hai phng din l c phiu khai thc ca cng ty cng li nhun nm gi BTC trc tip. Cc gng mt tiu biu i din cho phm vi ny l Marathon Digital Holdings, Hut 8 Mining Corp, Riot Blockchain, Inc. v Bitfarm Limited.\r\n\r\nKhi phn ln ngi dn, cc t chc v chnh ph bt u nhn ra Bitcoin khan him nh th no, th mt cp  FOMO hon ton mi (trng thi s b b l c hi) s xut hin. Cc t chc ch cn phn b 5% danh mc u t sang Bitcoin, BTC c th tng n 550.000 USD.\r\n\r\nDo , mt c sc ngun cung c th tr nn khng th trnh khi v khng c  ngun cung  p ng nhu cu tng mnh t nhng nh u t ln nh qu u c v Ngn hng Trung ng, khin gi tng vt cho