("928","1","2021-12-18 02:04:48","2021-12-18 02:04:48","<div class=\"style_thumbnailDescription__syRES style_ph50__1qq92\">\r\n<div class=\"style_textDescription__6qQQe\">\r\n<div class=\"style_thumbnailDescription__syRES style_ph50__1qq92\">\r\n<div class=\"style_textDescription__6qQQe\">Bi vit gip anh em hiu thm v nh ngha, vai tr ca Whitepaper trong vic u t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"post-detail-content\" class=\"style_postContentWrapper__2goJG style_ph50__1qq92 style_fontMedium__1ecko\">\r\n\r\nAnh em thng c nhng g khi tm c mt d n mi? Twitter, Medium hay website? Tt c u ng. Nhng c mt nhn vt khc cng kh quan trng m mnh ngh nhiu ngi cng  bit, nhng cha tht s hiu r v nh ngha hay vai tr,  l White Paper.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-0\">White Paper l g?</h2>\r\nWhite Paper l ti liu dng  m t cc thuc tnh ca d n mt cch chun nht, gip cng ng c ci nhn tng quan v d n. White Paper l ngun thng tin chun nht nu cn tham kho v bt k d n no.\r\n\r\nThut ng White Paper ra i trc khi c s dng trong Crypto. White Paper c ngun gc cch y khong mt th k,  ch bo co ngnh c xut bn bi mt s b ca chnh ph Vng quc Anh. Cn i vi Crypto, Whitepaper c l c bit n sm nht vo thi k ICO (<strong>Initial Coin Offering</strong>).\r\n<div>\r\n<figure><a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/LGMRF3NJSR.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-815\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/LGMRF3NJSR.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"736\" height=\"413\" /></a><figcaption>White Paper l g?</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\">White Paper cha nhng thng tin g?</h2>\r\nDi y l mt s thng tin thng thy ca mt White Paper ca cc d n trong Crypto:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>nh ngha v d n:</strong>Tm tt s lt nht ca mt d n.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>L do ra i ca d n:</strong>Gii quyt vn  no  ca th trng.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>C ch hot ng ca d n:</strong>Nu cc thnh phn, vai tr ca tng thnh phn trong d n, cc cng thc s dng trong hot ng,...</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>L trnh pht trin:</strong>Nhng vic team s lm trong tng lai.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Team:</strong>Gii thiu tng ngi, vai tr ca h trong d n.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thng tin v token.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cc token trong d n.</li>\r\n 	<li>vai tr mi token (thng thng ch c mt, nhng cc d n gn y c th c hai token vi vai tr khc nhau).</li>\r\n 	<li>S lng mi token.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chi tit m bn token chnh.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Nh u t ca d n.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTuy nhin, cc thng tin trn ch mang tnh ng vo thi im . Bi v cc thng tin trn c th d dng sa i da trn nhu cu thc t ca th trng, hoc thc lc ca i ng,...\r\n\r\n<em><strong>V d:Origin Protocol</strong>trc y lm v mng e-commerse. Tuy nhin, do trend NFT ang ln, v c v i ng d n c lm kh tt mng ny, nn h  i 100% mc tiu d n, White Paper t e-commerse sang mt d n lm v NFT. Hin ti, anh em nu ln trang ch ca Origin s khng thy bt k thng tin no lin quan n e-comerse.</em>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\">Chc nng ca White Paper</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"section-3\">Ni cha cc thng tin chun nht</h3>\r\nWhite Paper c th v nh gc ca mt d n. C th cc trang web Crypto s c cc gc nhn khc nhau v nh ngha d n, nhng nu c mt ni mt din gii chnh xc nht, th  l White Paper.\r\n\r\nTrong White Paper, chng ta c th tm thy gn nh mi thng tin chnh thng, gip vic u t ca anh em tr nn d dng hn.\r\n<h3 id=\"section-4\">Gi vn</h3>\r\nDo White Paper c xem nh bn phc tho d n trc khi bt tay vo lm, nn y l th tin quyt cn phi c  cc nh u t bit mnh ang b tin vo u. Tr v thi k ICO thnh hnh, cc d n a phn ch cn Whitepaper l c th i gi vn.\r\n\r\nNhng  thi im hin ti, White Paper khng cn qu quan trng trong vic gi vn. L do l v cc d n c v ra rt d trn giy, nhng bt tay vo lm th khng t nh k vng. Do , ngy nay cc nh u t thng nhn v i ng d n (sn phm trc , ti nng,...), d n  chy ri c kt qu nh th no,... T  mi ra quyt nh u t.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\">S khc nhau ca White Paper v Lite Paper</h2>\r\nNh mnh  ni, White Paper hin ti khng cn qu quan trng i vi mt d n. C l ngoi vic nh u t tr nn kh khn hn, l do khc l<strong>White Paper kh kh khan