("941","1","2021-12-19 03:42:46","2021-12-19 03:42:46","<strong>Ngi phn i tin in t ni bt nht ca Thng vin M v Gim c iu hnh Tesla Elon Musk, ang  gia mt cuc tranh lun gay gt trn Twitter.</strong>\n\nThng ngh s bang Massachusetts Elizabeth Warren gi Musk l k n bm v khng tr thu thu nhp, b nhn mnh lut thu ti sn yu cu Musk phi tr hng t USD tin thu.\n\nNgi n ng giu nht th gii  p tr, cho rng Thng vin Hoa K<em>xng ng vi ai  tt hn</em>Warren.\n\nMi chuyn bt u khi Johnna Crider, nh vn ca EVObsession v CleanTechnica, ln Twitter tit l rng Thng ngh s Warren ang mua qung co trn Facebook  nhm vo Elon Musk v ti trn thu.\n\nThng ngh s Hoa K cng b co buc  yu cu mi ngi ng gp 10  la cho chin dch tranh c ca c v khng nh rng Musk s c.\n\np li, ng ch Tesla cho bit Warren ang cho ngi M mt<em>li ni di v cng ln xn</em>v rng b l k n bm thc s, trong khi bn thn Musk  tr khon thu ln nht m mt c nhn tng tr trong lch s Hoa K.\n\nSau , ng hi liu Warren c phi l ngi m cng dn Hoa K thc s mong mun vi t cch l mt thng ngh s hay khng.\n\nng ch , Warren ang tranh c li gh Thng vin vo nm 2024. Tuy nhin, Musk tin rng bang Massachusetts xng ng c mt Thng ngh s tt hn.\n\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/elonmusk.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-914\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/elonmusk.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1086\" height=\"1171\" /></a>\n\niu ng ni l ngay c ngi ght Bitcoin, Peter Schiff, cng ln ting bnh vc Musk, ni rng Warren thc s l ngi n bm.\n<h2><strong>Cuc chin ca Warren v Bitcoin</strong></h2>\nThng ngh s Warren khng ch  kch Elon Musk m cn rt tch cc ch trch ngnh cng nghip tin in t.\n\nVo thng 7 nm nay, b  vit mt l th cho B trng Ti chnh Janet Yellen ku gi quy nh cht ch hn i vi lnh vc tin in t.\n\n<em>S cng iu, s bin ng, nhng tuyn b ngng cung ha ra li l sai. Khi th trng tin in t pht trin, ri ro i vi s n nh ti chnh v nn kinh t ca chng ta cng vy,</em>Warren tuyn b vo thi im .\n\nu thng ny, Elizabeth Warren ch trch cng ty khai thc Greenidge Generation c tr s ti New Yorkdo tc ng i vi mi trng v ngi tiu dng.\n\nTrc , Thng ngh s ny tweetrng<em>mt trong nhng iu d dng nht m chng ti c th lm l tiu dit cc loi tin in t lng ph mi trng.</em>\n\nWarren gn y  chorng stablecoin c ri ro nghim trng i vi ngi tiu dng v nn kinh t Hoa Kbi v chng ang <em>h tr mt trong nhng phn ti t nht ca th gii tin in t, DeFi, ni ngi tiu dng t c bo v nht khi b la o.</em>\n\nLiu Warren c ti c c vo nm 2024 hay khng? Chc chn cc c tri ng h tin in t s khng b phiu cho b.\n\nNgun: blogtienao.com","Ti sao Elon Musk ni Thng ngh s ni ting v chng crypto nn t chc?","","inherit","closed","closed","","938-revision-v1","","","2021-12-19 03:42:46","2021-12-19 03:42:46","","938","http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/?p=941","0","revision","","0"),
("942","1","2021-12-19 03:44:40","2021-12-18 20:44:40","<p class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Bitcoin (BTC) vth trng tin in t  chng kin s bin ng ng k vo cui nm, vi gi ca BTC gim mnh xung di mc 50.000  la trong nhng tun gn y.</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph\">Vi tnh hnh khng thun li hin ti, s ln Bitcoin b tuyn b l  cht tng ln 42 ln vo nm 2021, theo 99Bitcoins.</p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph\">S ln Bitcoin b tuyn b khai t vo nm 2021 nhiu gp 3 ln s ln nm 2020, tng cng l 14 ln.</p>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ezgif-4-0f8a9a3d4f.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1042\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ezgif-4-0f8a9a3d4f.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"978\" height=\"527\" /></a>\r\n\r\nc thnh lp vo nm 2010, trang web 99Bitcoins  hot ng nh mt kho lu tr chnh thc cho tt c cc ln ai  ni rng Bitcoin  hoc s cht. Trang web s dng cc tiu chun nghim ngt  ng ti ni dung.\r\n<p class=\"paragraph\">Mt s yu t c xem xt  xc nh c nn xut bn co ph trn trang web hay khng bao gm:</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Bn thn ni dung (khng phi ch c tiu ) phi r rng v thc t rng Bitcoin ang hoc s v gi tr (khng c c th ).</strong></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph\">Cc yu cu b sung i hi ni dung phi t mt ngi c lng ngi theo di ng k hoc mt trang web c s lng ngi truy cp cao.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Bitcoin c th tr nn v gi tr</strong></h2>\r\nTuyn b BTC s cht gn y nht c ghi nhn vo ngy 14 thng 12 nm 2021, vi gi Bitcoin l 46.612  la, ni dung c a ra bi Ph thng c Ngn hng Trung ng Anh, Sir Jon Cunliffe, ngi by t lo ngi rng s gia tng nhanh chng ca tin in t c th gy ra mi nguy him nghim trng i vi h thng ti chnh.\r\n<p class=\"paragraph\">Mt quan chc khc ca Ngn hng Trung ng Anh ni rng Bitcoin c th tr nn<em>v gi tr</em>v bt k ai u t vo BTC nn chun b  mt tt c nhng g h  u t.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Gio s ng knh cho bit Bitcoin c th khng tn ti lu</strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph\">Gio s xut sc v chnh sch quc t ti i hc Cornell, Eswar Prasad,  suy on rng s tn ti ca Bitcoin c th khng bn vng lu di.</p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph\">Theo Prasad, vic thiu hiu qu v khng c kh nng cho php trao i nh mt hnh thc thanh ton, c th khin Bitcoin bin mt.</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\r\n<blockquote class=\"td_pull_quote td_pull_center\"><strong>Bn thn Bitcoin c th khng tn ti lu hn na &lt;&gt; Vic s dng cng ngh blockchain ca Bitcoin khng hiu qu lm &lt;&gt; Do Bitcoin khng phc v tt nh mt phng tin trao i, ti khng ngh n s c bt k gi tr c bn no.</strong></blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph\">Bt chp s lng li tuyn b Bitcoin s cht tng mnh vo nm 2021, ROI Bitcoincho thy t l hon vn u t (% ROI) ca BTC so vi ng USD l 59,75% tnh n thi im hin ti (YTD).</p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph\">Hin ti, Bitcoin ang c giao dch  mc 46.895 USD, gim 0,18% trong 24 ngy qua v 3,35% so vi by ngy trc, vi tng gi tr th trng l 886 t USD.</p>\r\nNgun: blogtienao.com","Bitcoin b tuyn b cht 42 ln trong nm nay, gp 3 ln nm 2020","","publish","open","open","","bitcoin-bi-tuyen-bo-chet-42-lan-trong-nam-nay-gap-3-lan-nam-2020","","","2021-12-19 19:48:50","2021-12-19 12:48:50","","0","http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/?p=942","0","post","","0"),
