et\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">We are excited to announce that Clover chain is officially producing blocks as a <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Polkadot?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@Polkadot</a> Parachain today, marking a historic moment with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AcalaNetwork?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@AcalaNetwork</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MoonbeamNetwork?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@MoonbeamNetwork</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AstarNetwork?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@AstarNetwork</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ParallelFi?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ParallelFi</a></p>\r\nOnce again, thank you everyone who helped to make this happen. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%24CLV&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">$CLV</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%24DOT&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">$DOT</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/HctUMOJWNJ\">pic.twitter.com/HctUMOJWNJ</a>\r\n\r\n Clover Finance (@clover_finance) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/clover_finance/status/1472073062459711493?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">December 18, 2021</a></blockquote>\r\n<script src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\r\n<blockquote>Chng ti trn trng thng bo rng chui Clover  chnh thc to c block vi t cch l mt parachain trn Polkadot k t hm nay, nh du mt ct mc lch s cng vi Acala, Moonbeam, Astar v Parallel.\r\n\r\nMt ln na, xin c cm n tt c nhng ai  bin gic m ny tr thnh hin thc.</blockquote>\r\nPolkadot trc  nhn v nhiu ch trch v tr hon kh lu qu trnh pht trin parachain. Tuy nhin, vi thng tin ln ny, c th coi y l ct mc gip cng ng tin tng hn vi tm nhn cng nh cam kt ca d n.\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_119263\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-119263\"><a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DOT-18.12.21.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-931\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DOT-18.12.21.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1239\" height=\"759\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-119263\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"> th 1D ca cp DOT/USDT trn sn Binance vo lc 10:10 PM ngy 18/12/2021</figcaption></figure>\r\nD vy,  thi im bi vit,DOTvn cha c ng thi bay qu mnh, gi hin ang dao ng quanh vng 25 USD v vn ho th trng khong 27 t USD. iu ny l d hiu v nh hng chung ca ton th trng tin m ho trong nhng ngy gn y, cng nh vic lc mua DOT khng cn khi cc d n  chun b ngun lc trong giai on cui thng 10, u thng 11  tham gia u gi.\r\n\r\nGi DOT lc ny ang l 25.33 USD, gim hn mt na so vi mc ATH 55.09 USD lp vo u thng 11, thi imPolkadot chun b tin hnh cuc u gi parachain u tin.\r\n\r\nNh  c Coin68 gii thch, Polkadot nh l mt blockchain ca nhiu blockchain. D n ny s gip ngi dng c th xy dng blockchain ring trn h thng Polkadot mt cch d dng. Polkadot gi cc blockchain song song ny l parachain v cc parachain c th kt ni vi mng li chnh thng qua cc v tr  parachain slot. Nhng d n chin thngu gi parachains ginh c quyn thu v tr ny trong vng khong 2 nm, trc khi Polkadot t chc u gi li. Nh u t Polkadot c th tham gia ng h cho d n h mong mun ginh c slot parachain bng cchkha DOT li theo nh hng dn ny.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Polkadot-Auction-Vie.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-933\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Polkadot-Auction-Vie.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" /></a>\r\n\r\nNgun : <em><strong>Coin68</strong></em>","Parachain ca Polkadot chnh thc ln sng, k nguyn mi ca blockchain bt u?","","inherit","closed","closed","","945-revision-v1","","","2021-12-19 03:46:27","2021-12-19 03:46:27","","945","http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/?p=949","0","revision","","0"),
("950","1","2021-12-19 03:53:07","2021-12-18 20:53:07","<strong>Cu  nht phu nhn M Melania Trump tr thnh nhn vt ni ting tip theo cng b k hoch NFT trn blockchain Solana trong t ngy qua.</strong>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_119017\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-119017\">\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_940\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1500\"]<a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Melania-Trump.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-940\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Melania-Trump.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" /></a> FILE PHOTO: First lady Melania Trump hosts a roundtable discussion on Sickle Cell Disease inside the State Dining Room at the White House in Washington, U.S., September 14 2020. REUTERS/Tom Brenner[/caption]\r\n\r\n<figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-119017\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cu  nht phu nhn Melania Trump pht hnh NFT trn Solana</figcaption></figure>\r\nTheo thng bo ng ti vo ti ngy 16/12, cu  nht phu nhn Melania Trump s ra mt mt nn tng NFT ti a ch MelaniaTrump.com v pht hnh cc tc phm NFT theo thi gian. NFT u tin, mang tn Melanias Vision, s c m bn trong khong thi gian t ngy 16/12 n 31/12/2021.\r\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">Excited for this new venture, which combines my passion for art and commitment to helping our Nations children fulfill their own unique American Dream. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MelaniaNFT?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#MelaniaNFT</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/XJN18tMllg\">https://t.co/XJN18tMllg</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/wMpmDDsQdp\">pic.twitter.com/wMpmDDsQdp</a></p>\r\n MELANIA TRUMP (@MELANIATRUMP) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MELANIATRUMP/status/1471468919810670603?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">December 16, 2021</a></blockquote>\r\n<script src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\r\n\r\nB Melania Trump cho bit:\r\n<blockquote>Ti rt t ho c cng b  tng NFT ca mnh, i din cho am m ngh thut ca ti, vi s tin thu v s c dng cho chng trnh h tr tr em Be Best ca ti.</blockquote>\r\nMelanias Vision l mt bc tranh mu nc ca ha s Marc-Antoine Coulon, khc ha li i mt ca b Melania Trump. Gi bn NFT ca bc tranh ny l 1 SOL.\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_119018\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-119018\"><a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Melanias-Vision-1536x787-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-942\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Melanias-Vision-1536x787-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1536\" height=\"787\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-119018\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">NFT Melanias Vision</figcaption></figure>\r\nTrong nm 2022, b Trump s m bn thm cc NFT khc di dng tranh nh k thut s, tc phm ngh thut vt l v cc ph kin. Nhng NFT  u s c pht hnh trn blockchain Solana.\r\n\r\nNh vy, cu  nht phu nhn M l ngi ni ting mi nht cng b k hoch lm NFT trn Solana, saung sng lp nn tng livestream Twitchvhuyn thoi bng r Michael Jordan.\r\n\r\n chiu ngc li, cu Tng thng Donald Trump th nhiu ln ln ting ch trch tin m ha, v theo ng n e da n quyn lc ca ng  la M trong ngnh ti chnh.\r\n\r\n<strong>Cp nht:</strong>\r\n\r\nTrong nhng tuyn b a ra sau , c Solana Labs (n v pht trin Solana) v MoonPay (nh x l thanh ton c b Trump  cp trong thng bo) u ph nhn vic ch ng hp tc vi v cu  nht phu nhn  pht hnh NFT, khng nh y l hnh ng n phng t pha b Melania Trump.\r\n\r\nTrang Twitter chnh thc ca Solana  xa bi ng chia s li thng bo pht hnh NFT ca b Trump, cn i din Solana Labs tr li phng vn<em>Decrypt</em>nh sau:\r\n<blockquote>Chng ti mun lm r  trnh mi s hiu nhm rng vic b y la chn blockchain Solana l hon ton t pht v d n ny khng thuc bt k k hoch pht trin no ca Solana.</blockquote>\r\nTng t, MoonPay cng vit trn Twitter ca h:\r\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet tw-align-center\" data-twitter-extracted-i1639881285906396416=\"true\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">While we encourage everyone to be involved in Web 3.0, we would like to clarify that we are not partnered with Melania, nor can users purchase her collection using this payment method.</p>\r\n MoonPay (@moonpay)<a class=\"external\" href=\"https://twitter.com/moonpay/status/1471536039433019397?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">December 16, 2021</a></blockquote>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote>Mt bi bo ca Bloomberg mi y khng nh MoonPay l i tc pht hnh NFT ca cu  nht phu nhn Melania Trump. Thng tin ny l khng chnh xc v MoonPay khng c vai tr chnh thc no trong n lc y.\r\n\r\nTuy chng ti c lp trng khuyn khch tt c mi ngi n vi Web 3.0, chng ti mun lm r rng chng ti khng hp tc vi vi b Melania Trump, cng nh ngi dng s khng th tham gia mua NFT ca b y bng phng thc thanh ton ca chng ti.\r\n\r\nNgun: <em><strong>Coin68</strong></em></blockquote>","Cu  nht phu nhn Melania Trump pht hnh NFT trn Solana","","publish","open","open","","cuu-de-nhat-phu-nhan-melania-trump-phat-hanh-nft-tren-solana","","","2021-12-19 11:17:42","2021-12-19 04:17:42","","0","http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/?p=950","0","post","","0"),
