("954","1","2021-12-19 03:56:27","2021-12-18 20:56:27","Hm 17/12, Polygon (MATIC) v cng ty u t mo him Seven Seven Six ca Alexis Ohanian  cng b qu tr gi 200 triu USD  h tr cc d n c s kt hp gia mng x hi v Web 3.0. Sng kin ny s tp trung vo cc ng dng tr chi v nn tng truyn thng x hi c xy dng trn c s h tng ca Polygon.\r\n\r\nAlexis Ohanian l ng sng lp Reddit vo nm 2005, ng ri khi cng ty nm 2010 v sau  tr li gi v tr ch tch iu hnh vo nm 2014 trc khi t chc vo nm 2020. ng tng l nh u t seed ca mt s cng ty cng ngh v blockchain ni ting nh Coinbase, Instacart, Sky Mavis (ng sau Axie Infinity) v Patreon.\r\n\r\nL mt gii php m rng quy m Ethereum, h sinh thi ca Polygon  pht trin nhanh chng trong nm nay, vi hn 3.000 ng dng phi tp trung (Dapp) c xy dng trn mng ca mnh. u thng ny, Polygon thng bo  dnh ti 250 triu token MATIC, tr gi 627,5 triu USD vo thi im ,  pht trin cc cng ngh zero-knowledge dnh cho cc ng dng ti chnh phi tp trung phc tp. Vic ra mt giao thc v di chuyn cross-chain l nhng yu t chnh thc y gi MATIC trong nm nay.\r\n\r\nng sng lp Polygon, Sandeep Naiwal m t cc m hnh kinh doanh truyn thng x hi c tc ng su sc n th gii ca chng ta, c bit l da trn Web 3.0, mt khi nim rng dng  ch th h tip theo ca Internet. Thng qua Web 3.0, ngi dng to ra gi tr, kim sot mng v gt hi phn thng, ng ni.\r\n\r\nQuan h i tc vi Polygon khng phi l bc t ph u tin ca Ohanian trong vic pht trin Web 3.0. Nh  thng tin vo thng 11, nh ng sng lp Reddit  hp tc vi Solana Ventures  huy ng 100 triu USD cho cc sng kin Web 3.0 khc nhau.\r\n\r\nNgun: toiyeubitcoin.com","ng sng lp Reddit v Polygon ra mt qu 200 triu USD nhm ti Web 3.0","","publish","open","open","","dong-sang-lap-reddit-va-polygon-ra-mat-quy-200-trieu-usd-nham-toi-web-3-0","","","2021-12-19 11:17:36","2021-12-19 04:17:36","","0","http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/?p=954","0","post","","0"),
