("1041","1","2021-12-19 19:47:47","2021-12-19 12:47:47","<p class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Bitcoin (BTC) vth trng tin in t  chng kin s bin ng ng k vo cui nm, vi gi ca BTC gim mnh xung di mc 50.000  la trong nhng tun gn y.</strong></p>\n<p class=\"paragraph\">Vi tnh hnh khng thun li hin ti, s ln Bitcoin b tuyn b l  cht tng ln 42 ln vo nm 2021, theo 99Bitcoins.</p>\n<p class=\"paragraph\">S ln Bitcoin b tuyn b khai t vo nm 2021 nhiu gp 3 ln s ln nm 2020, tng cng l 14 ln.</p>\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/img_61beaaa88fe92.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-921\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/img_61beaaa88fe92.\" alt=\"\" width=\"978\" height=\"527\" /></a>\n\nc thnh lp vo nm 2010, trang web 99Bitcoins  hot ng nh mt kho lu tr chnh thc cho tt c cc ln ai  ni rng Bitcoin  hoc s cht. Trang web s dng cc tiu chun nghim ngt  ng ti ni dung.\n<p class=\"paragraph\">Mt s yu t c xem xt  xc nh c nn xut bn co ph trn trang web hay khng bao gm:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Bn thn ni dung (khng phi ch c tiu ) phi r rng v thc t rng Bitcoin ang hoc s v gi tr (khng c c th ).</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p class=\"paragraph\">Cc yu cu b sung i hi ni dung phi t mt ngi c lng ngi theo di ng k hoc mt trang web c s lng ngi truy cp cao.</p>\n\n<h2><strong>Bitcoin c th tr nn v gi tr</strong></h2>\nTuyn b BTC s cht gn y nht c ghi nhn vo ngy 14 thng 12 nm 2021, vi gi Bitcoin l 46.612  la, ni dung c a ra bi Ph thng c Ngn hng Trung ng Anh, Sir Jon Cunliffe, ngi by t lo ngi rng s gia tng nhanh chng ca tin in t c th gy ra mi nguy him nghim trng i vi h thng ti chnh.\n<p class=\"paragraph\">Mt quan chc khc ca Ngn hng Trung ng Anh ni rng Bitcoin c th tr nn<em>v gi tr</em>v bt k ai u t vo BTC nn chun b  mt tt c nhng g h  u t.</p>\n\n<h2><strong>Gio s ng knh cho bit Bitcoin c th khng tn ti lu</strong></h2>\n<p class=\"paragraph\">Gio s xut sc v chnh sch quc t ti i hc Cornell, Eswar Prasad,  suy on rng s tn ti ca Bitcoin c th khng bn vng lu di.</p>\n<p class=\"paragraph\">Theo Prasad, vic thiu hiu qu v khng c kh nng cho php trao i nh mt hnh thc thanh ton, c th khin Bitcoin bin mt.</p>\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\n<blockquote class=\"td_pull_quote td_pull_center\"><strong>Bn thn Bitcoin c th khng tn ti lu hn na &lt;&gt; Vic s dng cng ngh blockchain ca Bitcoin khng hiu qu lm &lt;&gt; Do Bitcoin khng phc v tt nh mt phng tin trao i, ti khng ngh n s c bt k gi tr c bn no.</strong></blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<p class=\"paragraph\">Bt chp s lng li tuyn b Bitcoin s cht tng mnh vo nm 2021, ROI Bitcoincho thy t l hon vn u t (% ROI) ca BTC so vi ng USD l 59,75% tnh n thi im hin ti (YTD).</p>\n<p class=\"paragraph\">Hin ti, Bitcoin ang c giao dch  mc 46.895 USD, gim 0,18% trong 24 ngy qua v 3,35% so vi by ngy trc, vi tng gi tr th trng l 886 t USD.</p>\nNgun: blogtienao.com","Bitcoin b tuyn b cht 42 ln trong nm nay, gp 3 ln nm 2020","","inherit","closed","closed","","942-autosave-v1","","","2021-12-19 19:47:47","2021-12-19 12:47:47","","942","http://localhost/wp/dc-ventures/?p=1041","0","revision","","0"),
